document.topic_text: August 22, 2016 Hyderabad Leave a comment Janab Syed Shaukat Ali s/o late Syed Hyder Ali died on August 21. Namaz-e-janaza was offered at Masjid Sultan Nawaz Jung, Aghapura Main Road after namaz-e-zohar followed by burial at ahata Tek ki Masjid. The late is survived by widow, five sons and seven daughters. Further information can be had on 9573669123 & 8686696532.
